item.title: yours
item.description:
The Deginner team has years of experience building everything from embedded systems and secure financial services to peer-to-peer (p2p) applications. Our software powers Coinapult, Crypto Capital, select Lamassu BTMs, and more.

If you have a project that you need help with, please contact us, below.
